- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses Support Vector Regression to train the model. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper discusses the challenges of social acceptance of eye-tracking technology. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with analyzing visual behavior through eye-tracking.
